<string id="bar_den_about_boltov_quest_1_first_talking_0">
    <text>Denis, I wanted to ask you something.</text>
</string>
<string id="bar_den_about_boltov_quest_1_first_talking_1">
    <text>Yes, of course, go ahead. What’s on your mind?</text>
</string>
<string id="bar_den_about_boltov_quest_1_first_talking_2">
    <text>Is it possible to create some kind of unique gun?</text>
</string>
<string id="bar_den_about_boltov_quest_1_first_talking_3">
    <text>Well, actually, I do have blueprints for one gun.</text>
</string>
<string id="bar_den_about_boltov_quest_1_first_talking_4">
    <text>Yeah? Tell me about it.</text>
</string>
<string id="bar_den_about_boltov_quest_1_first_talking_5">
    <text>Hmm, it’s called the Boltov. It uses the power of an artifact to recharge old rusty bolts and fires them.</text>
</string>
<string id="bar_den_about_boltov_quest_1_first_talking_6">
    <text>So you’re saying it’s theoretically possible to create a unique weapon?</text>
</string>
<string id="bar_den_about_boltov_quest_1_first_talking_7">
    <text>Yes, I’m sure I can make it happen. But I’ll need a lot of materials.</text>
</string>
<string id="bar_den_about_boltov_quest_1_first_talking_8">
    <text>I’m ready to help you as much as I can.</text>
</string>
<string id="bar_den_about_boltov_quest_1_first_talking_9">
    <text>Great, then first you’ll need to gather some materials.</text>
</string>
<string id="bar_den_about_boltov_quest_1_first_talking_10">
    <text>What exactly and how many?</text>
</string>
<string id="bar_den_about_boltov_quest_1_first_talking_11">
    <text>I’ll need ten Fastening Parts, five pieces of Scrap Metal, three Coils of Copper Wire, a Box of Capacitors, a Box of Resistors, and a Box of Transistors.</text>
</string>
<string id="bar_den_about_boltov_quest_1_first_talking_12">
    <text>Wow, that’s quite a list! Why so much?</text>
</string>
<string id="bar_den_about_boltov_quest_1_first_talking_13">
    <text>What did you expect? You think it’s that easy to create a working prototype? Consumables are called that for a reason.</text>
</string>
<string id="bar_den_about_boltov_quest_1_first_talking_14">
    <text>Alright, I’ll get everything you need.</text>
</string>
<string id="bar_den_about_boltov_quest_1_first_talking_15">
    <text>Also, you can bring me the materials as soon as you have the required amount of each type. You don’t need to collect everything and hand it in all at once.</text>
</string>    

<string id="bar_den_about_boltov_quest_1_second_talking_0">
    <text>About the materials...</text>
</string>
<string id="bar_den_about_boltov_quest_1_second_talking_00">
    <text>So, what have you got?</text>
</string>
<string id="bar_den_about_boltov_quest_1_second_talking_000">
    <text>Haven’t gathered anything yet...</text>
</string>
<string id="bar_den_about_boltov_quest_1_second_talking_1">
    <text>I’ve brought ten Fastening Parts.</text>
</string>
<string id="bar_den_about_boltov_quest_1_second_talking_2">
    <text>I’ve got five pieces of Scrap Metal.</text>
</string>
<string id="bar_den_about_boltov_quest_1_second_talking_3">
    <text>I’ve found three Coils of Copper Wire.</text>
</string>
<string id="bar_den_about_boltov_quest_1_second_talking_4">
    <text>Here’s the Box of Resistors.</text>
</string>
<string id="bar_den_about_boltov_quest_1_second_talking_5">
    <text>Here’s the Box of Transistors.</text>
</string>
<string id="bar_den_about_boltov_quest_1_second_talking_6">
    <text>Take the Box of Capacitors.</text>
</string>
<string id="bar_den_about_boltov_quest_1_second_talking_7">
    <text>Excellent, I’ll start assembling the prototype now.</text>
</string>
<string id="bar_den_about_boltov_quest_1_second_talking_8">
    <text>Alright, I’ll drop by again.</text>
</string>
<string id="bar_den_about_boltov_quest_1_second_talking_9">
    <text>I’ve brought everything you asked for.</text>
</string>
<string id="bar_den_about_boltov_quest_1_second_talking_10">
    <text>The prototype is ready.</text>
</string>
<string id="bar_den_about_boltov_quest_1_second_talking_11">
    <text>Alright, let’s see what you’ve got.</text>
</string>
<string id="bar_den_about_boltov_quest_1_second_talking_12">
    <text>Here, take it. And you’ll be able to buy ammo from me later.</text>
</string>

	
